---
// Balanced Responsive Card Layout for Core Benefits
---

<div class="core-benefits-section" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
  <div class="section-header">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-2">
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[#cc9933]"></span>
      <span class="text-[#cc9933] uppercase tracking-wider text-sm font-bold">
        Premium Experience
      </span>
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[#cc9933]"></span>
    </div>
    <h2
      class="text-4xl font-semibold text-[#003087] inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
    >
      <span class="w-2 h-10 bg-[#cc9933] rounded-full mr-3"></span>
      The USRad Advantage
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-[#003087] max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-10">
      We've reimagined medical imaging to deliver an experience that puts you
      first – at prices 30-70% below hospitals.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Balanced Responsive Grid Layout -->
  <div class="benefits-grid gap-y-10 items-stretch">
    <!-- Cards below use tighter padding and spacing -->
    <div
      class="benefit-card p-5 md:p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col$1hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-[1.02]"
    >
      <div class="benefit-icon mb-2">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-7 w-7 text-white"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="benefit-title text-base font-semibold mb-1">
        True Price Transparency
      </h3>
      <p class="benefit-description text-sm mb-3">
        See the exact price before you book – no hidden fees or surprise bills.
        Our all-inclusive pricing covers both facility and radiologist fees,
        with savings of 30–70% compared to hospital rates.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 mt-auto">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ All-inclusive pricing</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ No separate radiologist bills</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ No insurance required</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="benefit-card $1transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:bg-[#fdf6e9]"
    >
      <div
        class="benefit-tag text-xs bg-[#003087] text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded mb-2 inline-block"
      >
        2–4 Day Wait vs. Weeks
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-icon mb-2">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-7 w-7 text-white"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="benefit-title text-base font-semibold mb-1">
        Priority Scheduling
      </h3>
      <p class="benefit-description text-sm mb-3">
        Get your scan within 2–4 days instead of the typical 2–3 week wait. Our
        priority scheduling system gives you access to preferred appointment
        slots at state-of-the-art imaging centers.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ 2–4 day typical wait time</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Reserved priority slots</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Online scheduling</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="benefit-card p-5 md:p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1"
    >
      <div
        class="benefit-tag text-xs bg-[#003087] text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded mb-2 inline-block"
      >
        100% Board-Certified
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-icon mb-2">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-7 w-7 text-white"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="benefit-title text-base font-semibold mb-1">
        Radiologist-Guided Expertise
      </h3>
      <p class="benefit-description text-sm mb-3">
        Your scan is reviewed by a board-certified radiologist — and if your
        case requires it, it’s seamlessly escalated to a subspecialist with
        advanced training, ensuring accuracy without delays.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Subspecialty expertise</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Fellowship-trained physicians</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Scan-specific specialists</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="benefit-card p-5 md:p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between h-full transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-1"
    >
      <div class="relative mb-2">
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 text-[10px] bg-[#cc9933] text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded-bl-md uppercase font-semibold tracking-wide shimmer text-center"
        >
          Coming Soon
        </div>
      </div>
      <style>
        .shimmer {
          position: relative;
          overflow: hidden;
        }
        .shimmer::before {
          content: "";
          position: absolute;
          top: 0;
          left: -150%;
          width: 300%;
          height: 100%;
          background: linear-gradient(
            120deg,
            transparent,
            rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4),
            transparent
          );
          animation: shimmer-move 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes shimmer-move {
          0% {
            left: -150%;
          }
          100% {
            left: 100%;
          }
        }
      </style>
      <div class="benefit-icon mb-2">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-7 w-7 text-white"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="benefit-title text-base font-semibold mb-1">
        Streamlined Prescription Process
      </h3>
      <p class="benefit-description text-sm mb-3">
        We're developing partnerships with telehealth providers to simplify the
        path from prescription to imaging.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Virtual prescription options</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Cost-effective consultation</li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-1">✓ Simplified coordination</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Comparison Table (Optional) -->
<div class="comparison-banner mt-20" data-aos="fade-up">
  <!-- Comparison table content here if desired -->
</div>

<style>
  .core-benefits-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* Responsive Grid Layout */
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  /* Tablet: 2x2 Grid */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Extra Large Screens: All in a row */
  @media (min-width: 1280px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .benefit-card {
    position: relative;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border-top: 4px solid #cc9933;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  /* Corner Ribbon for Coming Soon */
  .ribbon {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ribbon-top-right {
    top: -10px;
    right: -10px;
  }

  .ribbon-top-right::before,
  .ribbon-top-right::after {
    border-top-color: transparent;
    border-right-color: transparent;
  }

  .ribbon-top-right::before {
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  .ribbon-top-right::after {
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
  }

  .ribbon-top-right span {
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
    right: -25px;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    width: 200px;
    background-color: #003087;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    padding: 5px 0;
  }

  /* Benefit Tags */
  .benefit-tag {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    background: #cc9933;
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background-color: #003087;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .benefit-card:hover .benefit-icon {
    background-color: #cc9933;
  }

  .benefit-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #003087;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .benefit-description {
    color: #003087;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-comparison {
    margin-top: auto;
    border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .comparison-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #003087;
  }

  .check-icon {
    color: #cc9933;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Coming Soon Badge */
  .coming-soon-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(0, 48, 135, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #003087;
  }

  .pulse-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background-color: #003087;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 8px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pulse-dot::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #003087;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% {
      transform: scale(1);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(2.5);
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
